WEBVTT

00:02:30.287 --> 00:02:32.966
I taught DeSean to read,

00:02:32.990 --> 00:02:38.291
but there are countless black boys
who remain trapped in illiteracy.

00:02:38.754 --> 00:02:41.168
According to the US
Department of Education,

00:02:41.192 --> 00:02:45.178
more than 85 percent
of black male fourth graders

00:02:45.202 --> 00:02:47.202
are not proficient in reading.

00:02:47.643 --> 00:02:48.888
85 percent!

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:55.399
The more challenges
to reading children face,

00:02:55.423 --> 00:02:58.471
the more culturally competent
educators need to be.

